726812f-a.title: Queens: Grand Central Parkwa - 82nd Road
726812f-a.text:
Grand Central Parkway, at 82nd Road and Smedley Street, showing a pond on the former J. Lott property (1873). The Parkway, when constructed will be right over the pond, which
will be filled in.
P. L. Sperr  March 23, 1927
